OL,3,CGuernsey States' tenants will not have
OL,4,Cto pay for carpets when moving
OL,6,FIslanders moving into Guernsey States'
OL,7,Fhousing will soon not have to provide
OL,8,Ftheir own carpets and other floor
OL,9,Fcoverings.
OL,11,FCurrently, similar to UK social
OL,12,Fhousing, it is standard practice for
OL,13,Fflooring to be missing when a new
OL,14,Ftenant moves in - regardless of the
OL,15,Fcondition or when it was last replaced.
OL,17,FThis was justified due to concerns
OL,18,Fover potential damage, hygiene and the
OL,19,Fcost of maintaining existing carpets.
