OL,3,CGuernsey States' tenants will not have
OL,4,Cto pay for carpets when moving
OL,6,FThe States have now decided, however,
OL,7,Fthat a "change is expected to be
OL,8,Fintroduced early next year", covering
OL,9,Fanyone "moving into, or transferring
OL,10,Fwithin, States' housing".
OL,12,FGuernsey States continues: "Existing
OL,13,Ffloor coverings that are in a suitable
OL,14,Fcondition will be left in situ, after
OL,15,Fbeing professionally cleaned where
OL,16,Fnecessary."
OL,18,FOtherwise, new flooring will be
OL,19,Fprovided free of charge.
