OL,3,CGuernsey States' tenants will not have
OL,4,Cto pay for carpets when moving
OL,6,FDeputy Tina Bury, President of the
OL,7,FEmployment and Social Security
OL,8,FCommittee, says: "I am really pleased
OL,9,Fto see the new Committee for Housing
OL,10,Fputting a solution in place.
OL,12,F"Private renters and Guernsey Housing
OL,13,FAssociation tenants are generally not
OL,14,Fexpected to provide their own floor
OL,15,Fcoverings when moving into a new
OL,16,Fproperty, so this levels the playing
OL,17,Ffield and brings the States in line
OL,18,Fwith standard practice as a modern
OL,19,Flandlord."
