OL,3,CGuernsey States' tenants will not have
OL,4,Cto pay for carpets when moving
OL,6,FDeputy Steve Williams, President of
OL,7,Fthe Housing Committee, adds: "I know
OL,8,FDeputy Bury and the previous Members
OL,9,Fof her Committee felt very strongly
OL,10,Fthat it was no longer acceptable to
OL,11,Fexpect tenants to move into properties
OL,12,Fwithout floor coverings and be
OL,13,Fexpected to take out loans or rely on
OL,14,Ffamily or charitable support."
OL,16,FThe Housing Committee is now looking
OL,17,Ffor quotes from potential suppliers of
OL,18,Ffloor coverings and assessing the
OL,19,Favailability of contractors before
OL,20,Fdeciding on an exact date for the
OL,21,Fchanges to take effect.
