OL,3,CGuernsey States' tenants will not have
OL,4,Cto pay for carpets when moving
OL,6,FThe move has been widely welcomed on
OL,7,Fsocial media, with one person saying:
OL,8,F"A friend paid to have a new wooden
OL,9,Ffloor in a States' apartment. When she
OL,10,Fleft, she had to destroy it, according
OL,11,Fto the rules. It is hard to understand
OL,12,Fwhy these were the rules at all."
OL,14,FAnother explains: "It's absolutely
OL,15,Finsane that people living in social
OL,16,Fhousing were being forced into debt to
OL,17,Fbuy their own carpets."
